â”‚       â”œâ”€â”€ macroscopic/       # LWR, CTM
â”‚       â”œâ”€â”€ hybrid/            # Adaptive simulation
â”‚       â”œâ”€â”€ gpu/               # Metal GPU acceleration
â”‚       â”œâ”€â”€ realdata/          # OSM parser, traffic APIs
â”‚       â”œâ”€â”€ python/            # Python bindings
â”‚       â””â”€â”€ examples/          # Example simulations
â”œâ”€â”€ python/
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ similar2logo/          # Python DSL
â”‚       â”œâ”€â”€ dsl/               # High-level API
